{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/etc./firebase-hosting/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jkun.io","author":"Jkun","siteUrl":"https://yilpe93.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4dde1ce2-26d0-554b-b9f8-39c498315fd6","excerpt":"Firebase Firebae는 모바일 앱, Web 앱을 개발하기 위한 통합 Backend 플랫폼 Push, Analytics, Storage, Auth, Hosting 등의 가양한 기능 제공 SDK 및 API 사용에 관한 전반적인 문서화가 잘되어 있고 한글 번역 품질 우수 HTTPS로 호스팅을 제공 Firebase SDK 설치 및 프로젝트 구성 Firebase Console 접속 후 Gmail 로그인 Firebase 프로젝트 생성 웹 앱에 Firebase 추가 생성된 script 코드를 HTML…","html":"<h2 id=\"firebase\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#firebase\" aria-label=\"firebase permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Firebase</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Firebae는 모바일 앱, Web 앱을 개발하기 위한 통합 Backend 플랫폼</li>\n<li>Push, Analytics, Storage, Auth, Hosting 등의 가양한 기능 제공</li>\n<li>SDK 및 API 사용에 관한 전반적인 문서화가 잘되어 있고 한글 번역 품질 우수</li>\n<li>HTTPS로 호스팅을 제공</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"firebase-sdk-설치-및-프로젝트-구성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#firebase-sdk-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EB%B0%8F-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"firebase sdk 설치 및 프로젝트 구성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Firebase SDK 설치 및 프로젝트 구성</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://console.firebase.google.com/\">Firebase Console</a> 접속 후 Gmail 로그인</li>\n<li>Firebase 프로젝트 생성</li>\n<li>웹 앱에 Firebase 추가</li>\n<li>생성된 script 코드를 HTML 하단에 복사 붙여넣기</li>\n<li>페이지 로딩 후 <code class=\"language-text\">Firebae Log</code> 출력 및 로딩여부 확인</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"firebase-features\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#firebase-features\" aria-label=\"firebase features permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Firebase Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Realtime DB: 데이터 조작에 관한 직관적인 API 제공, Firebase Storage와 연동 가능</li>\n<li>Storage: 이미지, 동영상 등 대용량 파일을 저장할 수 있는 공간</li>\n<li>Firebase Cloud Messaging: 기존 GCM 서비스에 Web 까지 커버하는 통합 푸시 메시지 서비스</li>\n<li>Authentication: Auth, SNS 연동 등의 인증 서비스 제공</li>\n<li>Hosting: Firebase에서 제공하는 무료 호스팅</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"firebase-hosting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#firebase-hosting\" aria-label=\"firebase hosting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Firebase Hosting</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-firebase-cli-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-firebase-cli-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"1 firebase cli 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Firebase CLI 설치</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g firebase-tools</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-firebase-console-에서-프로젝트-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-firebase-console-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"2 firebase console 에서 프로젝트 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. <a href=\"https://console.firebase.google.com/\">Firebase Console</a> 에서 프로젝트 생성</h3>\n<p>생성하고 나면 아래 웹 앱에서 Firebase 추가</p>\n<p><img src=\"./images/firebase/firebase-intro.png\" alt=\"./images/firebase/firebase-intro.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"3-firebase-프로젝트-초기화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-firebase-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%B4%88%EA%B8%B0%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"3 firebase 프로젝트 초기화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Firebase 프로젝트 초기화</h3>\n<p>위 프로젝트 생성 과정에서 웹 앱 추가 하고 나온 script를 프로젝트 <code class=\"language-text\">index.html</code> 하단에 복사 붙여넣기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/5.9.1/firebase-&lt;PackageName>.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>배포하려면 위 script 구문에 <code class=\"language-text\">-&lt;PackageName&gt;</code>을 추가적으로 넣어줘야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># google Login</span>\n$ firebase login\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># project directory</span>\n$ firebase init</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">init</code>명령어 실행하게 되면 아래 파일들이 생성되며 아래 정보가 정확히 들어가 있는지 확인해야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"># firebase.json\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"hosting\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"public\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[IndexRoot]\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"ignore\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"firebase.json\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"**/.*\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"**/node_modules/**\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># .firebaserc\n{\n  &quot;projects&quot;: {\n    &quot;default&quot;: &quot;[ProjectName]&quot;\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>Vue CLI와 firebase를 연동</p>\n<p><img src=\"./images/firebase/firebase-intro02.png\" alt=\"./images/firebase/firebase-intro02.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"4-firebase-deploy\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-firebase-deploy\" aria-label=\"4 firebase deploy permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Firebase deploy</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ firebase deploy</code></pre></div>\n<p>위 명령어를 입력하고 나면 해당 프로젝트가 hosting 되며, hosting url을 뱉는다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"./images/firebase/firebase-intro04.png\" alt=\"./images/firebase/firebase-intro04.png\"></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"ETC. Firebase와 Firebase Hosting하기","date":"March 28, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/etc./firebase-hosting/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Javascript/js-arrow-function/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ES6. Arrow Function","category":"Javascript","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/vue/vue-set-scss/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Vue. vue-cli에서 SCSS 적용과 Global SCSS 적용","category":"Vue","draft":false}}}}}